subSubSection.paragraph:
Prostomium slightly wider than long (
Fig. 28B
), or as long as wide (
Fig. 28E
), slightly wider anteriorly, lateral margins straight. Lateral antennae with ceratophores distinct, lateral antennae longer than prostomium, slightly longer than palps. Palpophores 3–4 times longer than palpostyles; median antenna short, inserted between posterior eyes, reaching prostomial centre.
